&lt;p&gt;Let's deploy all four.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;


  ğŸ“§ Layer 1: Budget Alerts with Terraform
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;aws_budgets_budget&lt;/code&gt; resource is the foundation. This sets up email alerts at 50%, 80%, and 100% of your monthly budget:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight hcl"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;resource&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;"aws_budgets_budget"&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;"monthly"&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class="nx"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;         &lt;span class="p"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;"${var.account_alias}-monthly-budget"&lt;/span&gt;
